{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd6db039a3","title":"杨成武对解放军测绘学院的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"76cbdfe8e0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":10,"articleId":"bd6db039a3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"杨成武","id":"e1397e909a","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"53bbb63fc8","name":"杨成武"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3d682c25ec","type":"title","text":"杨成武对解放军测绘学院的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75438ab8fb","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：18时〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"591d1e49b8","type":"paragraph","text":"学校大联合问题请李、王付总长抓一下，找测绘学院两派共同商量一下，让他们先行一步，做出个榜样来。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f61a621e5","type":"paragraph","text":"总参首长指示：","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c71bb5ac2f","type":"paragraph","text":"1、按班、队、系实行革命大联合和组成三结合领导班子。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"408b790ab3","type":"paragraph","text":"2、关于复课闹革命问题，首先要复毛泽东思想的课。学习最新指示。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"822c13c2a0","type":"paragraph","text":"商谈代表：两派派出相等数量的代表，各五人，主要勤务员要参加，包括参加组织的革命领导干部在内。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a571c7ebc4","type":"paragraph","text":"院、部、系的领导干部，双方马上协商，只要双方能够同意的都可参加（数量不限）。如果部里找不出适当人时，处的干部也可以，部的最好有人参加，特别是院务部和政治部要有领导干部参加。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bd6db039a3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}